\sum_{m=0}^n (m-np)^2 {n \choose m} p^m q^{n-m} = npq
(m-np)^2\binom n m=\{m(m-1)+(1-2np)m+n^2p^2\}\binom n m=n(n-1)\binom{n-2}{m-2}+(1-2np)n\binom {n-1}{m-1}+n^2p^2\binom n m
m\binom n m=m\frac{n!}{m!(n-m)!}=mn\frac{(n-1)!}{m\cdot(m-1)!\{(n-1)-(m-1)\}!}=n\binom{n-1}{m-1}
m\ge 1
m(m-1)\binom n m=m(m-1)\frac{n!}{m!(n-m)!}
=m(m-1)n(n-1)\frac{(n-1)!}{m(m-1)\cdot(m-2)!\{(n-2)-(m-2)\}!}=n(n-1)\binom{n-2}{m-2}
m\ge 2
